1 following the priorities for certain types of applicants under State law. The hiring shall not be
2 exempt from G.S. 126-14, 126-14.1, 126-14.5, and Articles 6 and 7 of this Chapter. The
3 exemption from this Chapter for the hiring process shall not affect whether the position is subject
4 to this Chapter once the employee is hired."
